1. -- {[%cal Ga1a3,Ge1a1][%csl Ga7]} { Putting a plug on the a-file enables White to get full control of the file because our plug prevents Black from doubling rooks while we can.

This theme comes from a classical game [/variation/41625743/#/24/w] between Karpov and Unzicker, which I consider one of the Ruy Lopez essential model games to study if you want to learn about this opening. } *

