{ This Quickstarter Guide is especially recommended for club-level players or even for facing opposition up to 2100 FIDE rating. It is also suitable for rapid and blitz play.

It consists of highly risky lines where we will often sacrifice material to obtain good attacking chances.

I have played these lines in rapid and blitz games quite successfully, by the way, and I encourage you to use this Quickstarter as a gateway to the rest of the repertoire if you like attacking chess and are not scared of complications. } 1. -- {[%mdl 32768]} *

