{ I have included in this Quickstarter Guide more solid variations we can use to obtain good positions without much risk. There are also some lines that offer us attacking prospects, but without running unnecessary risks.

As a gateway to the rest of the repertoire, this chapter is especially suitable for those looking for playable and comfortable positions without complicating matters, or face strong opposition, above 2100.

Logically, strong players should study the whole course to get a deeper knowledge of the opening, but this selection is a good starting point. } 1. -- {[%mdl 32768]} *

