19. O-O-O {[%cal Gd2b3,Gd1g1]} { Once the king is put into safety, we can resume our attack. } Ne6?! { When your opponent aligns a rook with your queen, stepping out before a discovered attack comes is a good policy. } 
20. Nc4 ( 20.Rxe5? Nf4 { winning. } ) Qe7 
